    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buddies in a Ball is a  co-op platformer where 1-4 friends are stuck inside of a metal ball together. Coordinate your movements, roll, jump, and scream your way through diverse levels. You're working against the clock, jeering announcers, and a ravenous audience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208260/extras/11a35a5eb14da93d2ec94f28b4a294e2.poster.avif?t=1768917635\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208260/extras/11a35a5eb14da93d2ec94f28b4a294e2.webm?t=1768917635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208260/extras/11a35a5eb14da93d2ec94f28b4a294e2.mp4?t=1768917635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Gameplay Elements:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Teamwork:</strong> 1-4 players control the ball together, communication and coordination are key.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Physics:</strong> Realistic rolling physics, speed, and momentum make every level a new challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dystopian world:</strong> The odd announcer, crazy advertisements, and jeering audience will keep you on your toes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Levels:</strong> Navigate ramps, tightropes, jumps, rotating platforms, flying objects, and more surprises.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Leaderboards:</strong> Compete to finish the game in the fastest time. Speed runners welcome!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Playable Characters:</strong> Pick the character that aligns with your personality.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208260/extras/b41441e1dc0f6f2c3df14d58f19242a3.poster.avif?t=1768917635\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208260/extras/b41441e1dc0f6f2c3df14d58f19242a3.webm?t=1768917635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208260/extras/b41441e1dc0f6f2c3df14d58f19242a3.mp4?t=1768917635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Modes:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free Roam: Access every level, unlimited respawns, explore the world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normal: Respawn at the beginning of the current level when you fall. Complete each level to unlock the next.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hardcore: One life. If you fall, restart from level one.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208260/extras/c2629532ebab10b81638da7053a42568.poster.avif?t=1768917635\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208260/extras/c2629532ebab10b81638da7053a42568.webm?t=1768917635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208260/extras/c2629532ebab10b81638da7053a42568.mp4?t=1768917635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
